921
00:45:32,561 --> 00:45:35,071
♪No need to question♪

922
00:45:36,961 --> 00:45:39,941
♪The truth and falsehood♪

923
00:45:39,941 --> 00:45:43,031
♪Needs to be discerned♪

924
